    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a few imperfections. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some typical wear and tear consistent with its age, such as minor oil seepage and occasional suspension noise. The exterior has some visible scratches and fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows standard signs of use on the seats and dashboard. Overall, it is a solid, drivable car that is priced to reflect its current state and any upcoming maintenance needs.",
      "price": 20000.0,
