    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. Mechanically, the engine runs well, but the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose and will likely need attention in the coming year. The exterior has some noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It has been regularly serviced, but expect to invest in some minor cosmetic and mechanical upkeep to bring it back to its best.",
